<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Creator Dashboard | 男人小性福</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                        display: ['Outfit', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                    colors: {
                        brand: {
                            50: '#fff1f2',
                            100: '#ffe4e6',
                            200: '#fecdd3',
                            300: '#fda4af',
                            400: '#fb7185',
                            500: '#f43f5e',
                            600: '#e11d48',
                            700: '#be123c',
                            800: '#9f1239',
                            900: '#881337',
                            accent: '#ff2d55',
                        },
                        slate: {
                            950: '#020617',
                        }
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'gradient-x': 'gradient-x 15s ease infinite',
                        'float': 'float 6s ease-in-out infinite',
                    },
                    keyframes: {
                        'gradient-x': {
                            '0%, 100%': { 'background-size': '200% 200%', 'background-position': 'left center' },
                            '50%': { 'background-size': '200% 200%', 'background-position': 'right center' },
                        },
                        'float': {
                            '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)' },
                            '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-20px)' },
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #020617;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.15) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 100% 0%, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1) 0px, transparent 50%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .glass-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-color: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 30%, #fb7185 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .bento-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="font-sans antialiased overflow-x-hidden p-4 md:p-8">

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2 mr-1">
                    <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-brand-400 opacity-75"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-brand-500"></span>
                </span>
                Brainstorming Engine V2.0
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-extrabold tracking-tight gradient-text">
                Video Idea Generator
            </h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl text-lg">
                为您的品牌 <span class="text-brand-400 font-semibold">男人小性福</span> 量身定制的创意灵感库。
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <button class="px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-500 text-white font-semibold transition-all shadow-lg shadow-brand-600/20 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
                </svg>
                新创意
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bento-grid">
            
            <!-- Section 1: Channel Profile -->
            <section class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem] h-fit">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-brand-500/30">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">Your Channel Profile</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/5">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 font-bold mb-1">品牌定位</p>
                            <p class="text-slate-200 leading-relaxed font-medium">男人小性福</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/5">
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 font-bold mb-1">核心支柱</p>
                            <p class="text-slate-200 leading-relaxed">聚焦女性美感、热门舞蹈挑战、为男性受众提供视觉愉悦与生活小确幸。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 2: Topics -->
                <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-6">Key Topics</h2>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 text-sm font-medium">#热门舞蹈挑战</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">#视觉美学</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">#卡点变装</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">#生活小确幸</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">#4K超清</span>
                        <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">#反差感</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3: Brainstormed Video Ideas -->
            <section class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                
                <!-- Category 1 -->
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 ml-2">
                        <span class="h-8 w-1 bg-brand-500 rounded-full"></span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-slate-100 uppercase tracking-wide">视觉美学派 (Visual Aesthetic)</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden group">
                            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-500/10 rounded-full -mr-16 -mt-16 blur-2xl group-hover:bg-brand-500/20 transition-all"></div>
                            <span class="text-brand-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Idea 01</span>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">暮光之境 (Twilight Flow)</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">日落时分落地窗前，利用黄金时刻光影。身着真丝长裙，动作舒缓有力，强调线条美。</p>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase">Hooks</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-2">
                                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-300 italic">
                                        <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1">✦</span> “这一刻，只想让你静静欣赏这份极致的温柔。”
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden group">
                            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-500/10 rounded-full -mr-16 -mt-16 blur-2xl group-hover:bg-brand-500/20 transition-all"></div>
                            <span class="text-brand-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Idea 02</span>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">暗黑赛博 (Cyber Silhouette)</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">全黑背景，霓虹灯勾勒身形。随重低音鼓点，通过光影闪烁展现力量感与神秘感。</p>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase">Hooks</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-2">
                                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-300 italic">
                                        <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1">✦</span> “4K超清预警：建议全屏观看，感受光影下的呼吸。”
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Category 2 -->
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 ml-2">
                        <span class="h-8 w-1 bg-brand-500 rounded-full"></span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-slate-100 uppercase tracking-wide">快节奏变装派 (Trend Fast-Paced)</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl group">
                            <span class="text-brand-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Idea 03</span>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">职场与午夜 (Office to Night)</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">正式西装处理文件，瞬间提速变装至拉丁舞裙，由拘束转为狂热。</p>
                            <div class="bg-black/20 p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 space-y-2">
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Engagement Hook</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-200">“答应我，一定要看到最后那一秒，好戏在后头。”</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl group">
                            <span class="text-brand-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Idea 04</span>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">色彩心情 (Color Mood Palette)</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">每3秒切换一套不同色系穿搭，每套服装对应一段舞蹈，高速剪辑目不暇接。</p>
                            <div class="bg-black/20 p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 space-y-2">
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-tighter">Engagement Hook</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-200">“你更喜欢哪一个颜色的我？评论区告诉我。”</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Category 3 -->
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 ml-2">
                        <span class="h-8 w-1 bg-brand-500 rounded-full"></span>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-slate-100 uppercase tracking-wide">微剧情舞蹈派 (Storytelling)</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <span class="text-brand-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Premium Concept</span>
                            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">居家小确幸 (The "Girlfriend" POV)</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">镜头模拟男友视角。舞者系围裙在厨房忙碌，转身发现镜头羞涩一笑，随即开始甜美居家舞，展现平凡幸福。</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-brand-600/20 text-brand-300 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold border border-brand-500/30">
                                    HIGH RETENTION
                                </div>
                                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold border border-white/10">
                                    EMOTIONAL CONNECT
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-brand-500/20">
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-400 uppercase mb-4">Hook Strategy</p>
                            <ul class="space-y-3">
                                <li class="text-sm text-slate-200 flex gap-2">
                                    <span class="text-brand-500">✔</span> “其实，我私下里还有另一面，你想看吗？”
                                </li>
                                <li class="text-sm text-slate-200 flex gap-2">
                                    <span class="text-brand-500">✔</span> “如果你的女朋友突然这样对你...”
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Success Indicator Floating -->
    <div class="fixed bottom-8 right-8 animate-float">
        <div class="bg-brand-600 p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-brand-600/40 border border-brand-400/50 flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
            <div class="bg-white/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Ready to Filming?</p>
                <p class="text-brand-100 text-xs">Explore these 6 curated ideas</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Simple interactivity for cards
        document.querySelectorAll('.glass-card').forEach(card => {
            card.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
                // Potential for adding subtle sound effects or logic here
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
